On initial checkout do the following:
ln -s todo.txt ChangeLog
ln -s todo.txt NEWS
autoreconf
automake --add-missing
autoreconf

Set values correctly at top of src/Makefile.am for OOPSHOME etc.
Set name of ampl executable at top of ampl.tab.ypp.
Set amplsolver path in configure.ac and rerun autoreconf

Compilation:
./configure
make
